---
title: "Slade Networks — UniFi Installation & Support, Finger Lakes NY"
description: "Professional UniFi network installation and ongoing support for homes and small businesses in the Finger Lakes, NY. Wi-Fi, cameras, phones — free consultation."
navActive: home
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block pageStyles %}
  <style>
    /* ── Services preview ── */
    .servicesPreview {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .serviceCard {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      transition: transform .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease);
    }
    .serviceCard:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
      border-color: var(--primary-100);
    }

    .serviceCard h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }

    .serviceCard p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      line-height: 1.65;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .serviceCard .media {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 90px;
    }

    .serviceCard .media img {
      width: 55%;
      max-width: 180px;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
      transition: transform .3s var(--ease);
    }

    .serviceCard:hover .media img {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .servicesFooter {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .servicesFooter .seeAll {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── Process steps (compact) ── */
    .processSteps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .processStep {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      padding: 24px;
      transition: transform .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease);
    }

    .processStep:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      border-color: var(--primary-100);
    }

    .stepNum {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: var(--r-md);
      background: var(--primary-50);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary-100);
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .processStep h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }

    .processStep p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .processFooter {
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    /* ── Meet Andrew (compact) ── */
    .meetSection { padding: 0 0 72px }

    .meetCompact {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .meetPhoto {
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--gray-50);
    }

    .meetPhoto img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      display: block;
    }

    .meetContent {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .meetRole {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary);
      letter-spacing: .03em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }

    .meetContent p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    @media(max-width:980px) {
      .processSteps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr }
    }

    @media(max-width:700px) {
      .meetCompact { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px }
      .meetPhoto { width: 120px; height: 120px }
    }

    /* ── Service area (compact) ── */
    .serviceAreaCompact {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .serviceAreaMapSmall {
      width: 260px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .serviceAreaMapSmall img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      object-fit: contain;
      background: var(--gray-50);
    }

    .serviceAreaText {
      flex: 1;
    }

    @media(max-width:700px) {
      .servicesPreview { grid-template-columns: 1fr }
      .processSteps { grid-template-columns: 1fr }
      .serviceAreaCompact { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px }
      .serviceAreaMapSmall { width: 100%; max-width: 280px }
    }
  </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <main>

    {# ── HERO ── #}
    <section class="hero heroDark">
      <div class="heroBackground">
        <img src="/assets/IMG_0431.jpeg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="eager">
      </div>
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="heroBadge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          Owner-operated &mdash; Finger Lakes, NY
        </div>
        <h1>Professional Networks for Homes and Businesses</h1>
        <p class="subtext">
          Wi-Fi, cameras, and phone systems designed for your space — installed cleanly, built to last, and backed by someone local who picks up the phone.
        </p>
        <div class="heroButtons">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Get a free consultation</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/services/">View services</a>
        </div>

        <div class="trustBar">
          <div class="trustItem">
            <div class="trustIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            Cisco CCNA certified
          </div>
          <div class="trustItem">
            <div class="trustIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            CS degree, St. Bonaventure
          </div>
          <div class="trustItem">
            <div class="trustIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            One person. Every job.
          </div>
          <div class="trustItem">
            <div class="trustIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
            </div>
            Free on-site consultation
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── SERVICES PREVIEW ── #}
    <section class="section sectionAlt reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">What we install</p>
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">Wi-Fi, Cameras, and Phones — All in One System</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro">
          Every install runs on UniFi — enterprise-grade equipment at residential prices. One platform, one dashboard, no juggling vendors.
        </p>

        <div class="servicesPreview reveal-stagger">
          <div class="serviceCard">
            <h3>Wi-Fi</h3>
            <p>Access points planned for your layout, installed cleanly, and verified for full coverage — living areas, offices, outdoor spaces. No dead spots.</p>
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/assets/u7-pro-xg-2.png" alt="UniFi Wi-Fi access point" loading="lazy">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="serviceCard">
            <h3>Cameras</h3>
            <p>Strategic placement, no blind spots, footage accessible from your phone. Angles, recording, and remote playback confirmed before we leave.</p>
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/assets/uvc-g6-pro-turret-10.png" alt="UniFi security camera" loading="lazy">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="serviceCard">
            <h3>VoIP Phones</h3>
            <p>Business phone systems on UniFi Talk — number porting handled, clean cutover, and tested end-to-end. Calls are clear, phones just work.</p>
            <div class="media">
              <img src="/assets/utp-g3-touch-enterprise-1.png" alt="UniFi Talk desk phone" loading="lazy">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="servicesFooter">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/services/">See all services</a>
          <a class="seeAll" href="/services/">Cabling, switching, racks, failover, and more &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── TESTIMONIAL ── #}
    <section class="testimonialBand reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">What clients say</p>
        <span class="quoteMark" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
        <p class="quoteText">His professionalism and calm, practical problem-solving ability were consistently impressive. His work has had a meaningful impact on the Museum's operations and visitor experience.</p>
        <p class="quoteAttrib">&mdash; The Finger Lakes Boating Museum</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── INSTALL PHOTOS ── #}
    <section class="section reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">From the field</p>
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">See the work up close</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro">
          Clean installs, organized racks, professional results — every project in the Finger Lakes.
        </p>

        <div class="scrollWrapper" aria-label="Install photos carousel">
          <div class="productScroll">
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0465.jpeg" alt="Wi-Fi access point mounted on ceiling" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/camera-install.jpeg" alt="Security camera installed on building exterior" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0464.jpeg" alt="VoIP desk phone configured and ready" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0431.jpeg" alt="Clean, organized network rack after installation" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0248.jpeg" alt="UniFi access point installed flush in commercial drop ceiling" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0190.jpeg" alt="UniFi Talk desk phone deployed on conference room table" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0474.jpeg" alt="Security camera mounted on historic stone wall" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0476.jpeg" alt="UniFi access point installed in stone wine cellar" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0478.jpeg" alt="UniFi access point installed in drop ceiling above ship's store" loading="lazy"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0481.jpeg" alt="Security camera mounted on interior wall near local artwork" loading="lazy"></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── HOW IT WORKS ── #}
    <section class="section reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">The process</p>
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">Simple from start to finish</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro">
          No surprises, no guesswork. Here's exactly what happens when you reach out.
        </p>

        <div class="processSteps reveal-stagger">
          <div class="processStep">
            <div class="stepNum">1</div>
            <h3>Free on-site visit</h3>
            <p>We come to you, walk the space, and understand what you need — no phone-call estimates, no guessing from a floor plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="processStep">
            <div class="stepNum">2</div>
            <h3>Written quote</h3>
            <p>You get a detailed plan and itemized quote in writing before any work begins. No vague estimates, no surprises at the end.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="processStep">
            <div class="stepNum">3</div>
            <h3>Clean installation</h3>
            <p>Equipment installed neatly — cables routed properly, gear mounted cleanly, everything labeled for easy future service.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="processStep">
            <div class="stepNum">4</div>
            <h3>Handoff and support</h3>
            <p>Everything verified before we leave. You get full admin access and a walkthrough. Ongoing support plans available.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="processFooter reveal">
          <a class="btn" href="/process/">See the full process &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── MEET ANDREW ── #}
    <section class="meetSection sectionAlt reveal" style="padding: 48px 0">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="meetCompact">
          <div class="meetPhoto reveal">
            <img src="/assets/Headshot.jpg" alt="Andrew Slade, founder of Slade Networks" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="meetContent reveal">
            <p class="sectionLabel">Who you're working with</p>
            <h2 class="sectionTitle" style="margin-bottom:6px">Andrew Slade</h2>
            <p class="meetRole">Founder &amp; Owner</p>
            <p>
              Every consultation, install, and support call is handled by one person — no subcontractors, no middlemen. CCNA certified, CS degree from St. Bonaventure, based in Penn Yan.
            </p>
            <div style="margin-top:18px;">
              <a class="btn" href="/about/">More about Andrew &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── SERVICE AREA ── #}
    <section class="section reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="serviceAreaCompact">
          <div class="serviceAreaMapSmall">
            <img src="/assets/Updated_service_area.jpg" alt="Slade Networks service area map covering the Finger Lakes and surrounding Upstate NY region" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="serviceAreaText">
            <p class="sectionLabel">Service area</p>
            <h2 class="sectionTitle">Based in Penn Yan, Serving the Finger Lakes</h2>
            <p class="sectionIntro" style="margin-bottom:0">Rochester to Corning, Ithaca to Canandaigua — and everywhere in between. Outside the map? Reach out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── CTA ── #}
    <section class="ctaSection reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="ctaInner">
          <div>
            <h2>Ready to fix your network?</h2>
            <p>Book a free on-site consultation. We'll walk the space, understand your needs, and deliver a written quote — no strings attached.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ctaButtons">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Get started</a>
            <a class="btn" href="mailto:info@sladenetworks.com">Email us directly</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
{% endblock %}
